Siapkan keberangkatan darurat.

62
00:04:29,177 --> 00:04:30,220
Komandan?

63
00:04:30,303 --> 00:04:32,139
Kita batalkan. Itu perintah.

64
00:04:42,733 --> 00:04:45,277
Berapa lama menjelang
lepas landas, Martinez?

65
00:04:45,444 --> 00:04:46,486
12 menit.

66
00:04:46,653 --> 00:04:49,698
TANGGAL MISI - HARI KE
-18 HABITAT RUANG HAMPA

67
00:04:50,073 --> 00:04:51,408
Jarak pandang hampir nol.

68
00:04:51,575 --> 00:04:53,869
Jika ada yang tersesat,
ikuti telemetri kostumku.

69
00:04:54,035 --> 00:04:55,036
Kau siap?

70
00:04:55,120 --> 00:04:56,371
Siap.

71
00:04:58,790 --> 00:05:01,585
- Komandan, kau tak apa-apa?
- Aku baik-baik saja.

72
00:05:09,468 --> 00:05:10,927
KAMERA LEWIS

73
00:05:25,817 --> 00:05:28,737
Komandan, kita pada 10 derajat, dan
MAV akan terbalik pada 12,3 derajat.

74
00:05:29,362 --> 00:05:32,449
Mungkin kita bisa
mencegah MAV terbalik.

75
00:05:32,616 --> 00:05:33,617
Caranya?

76
00:05:34,075 --> 00:05:37,078
Gunakan kabel dari tiang
komunikasi sebagai penahan,

77
00:05:37,245 --> 00:05:38,914
lalu ikatkan ke Rover.

78
00:05:39,247 --> 00:05:40,290
Awas!

79
00:05:43,627 --> 00:05:44,628
Watney!

80
00:05:44,794 --> 00:05:46,171
KAMERA WATNEY

81
00:05:46,296 --> 00:05:48,673
Peringatan. Kebocoran
kostum terdeteksi.

82
00:05:48,757 --> 00:05:49,799
Apa yang terjadi?

83
00:05:49,883 --> 00:05:52,010
- Dia kena puing.
- Watney, melapor.

84
00:05:52,802 --> 00:05:54,846
Alarm dekompresinya
menyala sebelum telemetri mati.

85
00:05:55,013 --> 00:05:57,307
- Di mana terakhir melihatnya?
- Aku tak tahu posisinya.

86
00:05:57,474 --> 00:05:59,309
- Status vital kostumnya?
- Sinyal terputus.

87
00:05:59,476 --> 00:06:00,894
Sinyal Watney terputus.

88
00:06:01,061 --> 00:06:02,187
- Beck!
- Ya.

89
00:06:02,354 --> 00:06:04,606
Berapa lama dia bisa
bertahan dalam dekompresi?

90
00:06:04,814 --> 00:06:06,066
Kurang dari semenit.

91
00:06:06,525 --> 00:06:08,693
Berbaris, berjalan ke barat.

92
00:06:08,860 --> 00:06:10,820
Mungkin dia berbaring,
jangan diinjak.

93
00:06:12,656 --> 00:06:13,865
Komandan...

94
00:06:14,032 --> 00:06:15,659
Kita pada posisi 10,5 derajat.

95
00:06:15,825 --> 00:06:16,826
Miring berlebihan.

96
00:06:16,993 --> 00:06:19,788
Miring ke 11 derajat
karena embusan angin.

97
00:06:20,080 --> 00:06:21,331
Diterima.

98
00:06:21,498 --> 00:06:23,875
Semuanya, ikuti
sinyal kostum Martinez.

99
00:06:24,042 --> 00:06:26,044
Kau akan di ruang kedap
udara. Bersiap meluncur.

100
00:06:26,378 --> 00:06:27,712
Bagaimana denganmu, Komandan?

101
00:06:27,879 --> 00:06:30,549
Aku mau mencari
sebentar. Cepatlah!

102
00:06:31,007 --> 00:06:32,008
Pergi!

103
00:06:35,679 --> 00:06:36,805
Watney!

104
00:06:37,305 --> 00:06:38,890
Watney, melapor!

105
00:06:39,057 --> 00:06:41,142
MAV pada posisi 11,6 derajat.

106
00:06:41,268 --> 00:06:42,644
Satu embusan
kuat, kita terbalik.

107
00:06:43,228 --> 00:06:44,563
Jika terbalik, kau meluncur.

108
00:06:44,729 --> 00:06:46,064
Pikirmu aku mau meninggalkanmu?

109
00:06:46,231 --> 00:06:47,774
Itu perintah, Martinez.

110
00:06:48,608 --> 00:06:49,734
Mark!

111
00:06:50,694 --> 00:06:53,071
Mark! Kau dengar?

112
00:06:55,282 --> 00:06:58,034
Martinez, bagaimana
dengan radar pelacak jarak?

113
00:06:58,243 --> 00:06:59,911
Itu bisa melacak kostum Watney?

114
00:07:00,078 --> 00:07:01,413
Ini untuk lihat
Hermes dari orbit

115
00:07:01,580 --> 00:07:03,456
dan bukan logam kecil
dari sebuah kostum.

116
00:07:03,623 --> 00:07:04,624
Cobalah.

117
