mendekati lokasi misi Ares 3 di Mars.

148
00:09:24,848 --> 00:09:28,518
Pukul 6.45, badai memburuk

149
00:09:28,601 --> 00:09:31,438
dan kami tak punya pilihan
selain membatalkan misi.

150
00:09:31,604 --> 00:09:34,065
Berkat reaksi cepat
Komandan Lewis,

151
00:09:34,149 --> 00:09:37,277
astronaut Beck, Johanssen,
Martinez dan Vogel,

152
00:09:37,444 --> 00:09:40,238
semua berhasil tiba
di Mars Ascent Vehicle

153
00:09:40,321 --> 00:09:43,324
dan melakukan peluncuran
darurat pukul 7.28 Waktu Tengah.

154
00:09:43,408 --> 00:09:45,243
