ARES III AKAN PULANG

155
00:09:45,410 --> 00:09:47,704
Sayangnya, dalam evakuasi,

156
00:09:47,787 --> 00:09:52,042
astronaut Mark Watney
terkena puing dan tewas.

157
00:09:53,126 --> 00:09:55,003
Komandan Lewis
dan seluruh regunya

158
00:09:55,170 --> 00:09:59,799
berhasil mencapai Hermes
dan kini dalam perjalanan pulang.

159
00:09:59,966 --> 00:10:02,343
Namun, Mark Watney tewas.

160
00:10:02,635 --> 00:10:04,137
Direktur Sanders!

161
